onDiagnosticsError.prompt:
New TS error in {{file}}:

{{diagnostics}}

Steps: (1) getHover at the error position to fetch expected vs actual types; (2) if the error references a symbol, goToTypeDefinition or explainSymbol to ground it; (3) describe the root cause in one sentence; (4) propose the exact patch (file + line range + replacement). Do NOT call editText — propose only.
